        "timestamp": "2020-04-28 12:18:22.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> Good work removing that Either. Have you checked exception\\error flow as well?\n\nHi,\n\nThe either is technically not removed, I have just refactored the code so it is better used, so the flow has not changed. I only leveraged the composition capabilities of Either by using `left().map`, which enables us to apply a function on the left value only if the Either in question is actually a left. Otherwise, the function is never applied.",
